result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="通知单编号"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="Number"
        v-decorator="[
          'id',
          {
            rules:[
              { required: true, message: '请输入通知单编号' },
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.id : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
     <a-form-item
      label="部位"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'part',
          {
            rules:[
              { required: true, message: '请输入部位' },
              { max:128, message: '长度在128个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.part : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
   <a-form-item
          label="发出日期"
          :label-col="{span: 6}"
          :wrapper-col="{span: 18}">
          <a-date-picker
            style="width:100%"
            v-decorator="[
              'give_time',
              {rules: [{type: 'object',required: true, message: '请选择发出日期'}]}
            ]"></a-date-picker>
        </a-form-item>
     <a-form-item
          label="回复日期"
          :label-col="{span: 6}"
          :wrapper-col="{span: 18}">
          <a-date-picker
            style="width:100%"
            v-decorator="[
              'reply_time',
              {rules: [{type: 'object',required: true, message: '请选择回复日期'}]}
            ]"></a-date-picker>
        </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
